## Static Assets Setup

The application requires a background image for the hero section. Place a file named `weather-bg.jpg` in the `static/images/` directory.

You can download a suitable weather-themed background image from:
- Unsplash: https://unsplash.com/s/photos/weather-rain
- Pexels: https://www.pexels.com/search/weather/

Or create a simple gradient background by using the CSS fallback already implemented.